Responsibilities Automation.Process automation: Automatically collect stakeholder requirements via online forms and surveys.
Responsibilities Automation.Description: An automated workflow sends out digital surveys/forms to stakeholders, collects responses in a central repository (e.g., a Google Sheet), and aggregates the data to inform the blueprint design process.

Responsibilities Automation.Process automation: Automatically generate a preliminary blueprint draft using design templates and AI assistance.
Responsibilities Automation.Description: Use a pre-defined design template in your CAD or design tool, then trigger an automation that fills in the template with the collected requirements. AI (e.g., ChatGPT) can help generate textual descriptions or design annotations.

Responsibilities Automation.Process automation: Automatically update the blueprint based on change requests tracked in a feedback system using predefined rules.
Responsibilities Automation.Description: Integrate a feedback collection tool (e.g., an online form or issue tracker) to capture change requests. Once approved, an automated process updates the blueprint using version control or direct integration with the design software.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically monitor and retrieve management messages related to interview assignments.
Task Automation.Tools/Comments: Email API, Slack integration, Make, Zapier
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Set up an automation to monitor a designated email inbox or messaging channel for incoming management messages about interview assignments, triggering notifications or actions based on predefined keywords or tags.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically generate and store interview requirement documents using templates.
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Trigger an automation when a new interview assignment is received that populates a predefined document template with interview requirements and saves it in a shared repository (e.g., Google Drive).

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically apply candidate filters within the CRM based on predefined criteria.
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Configure the CRM to execute API calls with specific filter parameters (e.g., skills, experience) to update and refresh the candidate list automatically for the interview process.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically extract and copy candidate contact information from the CRM.
Task Automation.Tools/Comments: CRM API, Data extraction tools, Zapier
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Set up an automation to pull candidate contact details from the CRM and populate them into a structured format (such as a spreadsheet or contact management system) for easy access and further processing.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically generate a unique interview meeting link.
Task Automation.Tools/Comments: Google Calendar/Meet API, Zoom API, Make, Zapier
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Configure an automation that calls the meeting platform's API to create a new interview link upon scheduling an interview, then store or forward the link to the relevant communication channels.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically send an interview invitation via email or messaging platform.
Task Automation.Tools/Comments: Email API, Messaging services, Make, Zapier
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Trigger an automation upon scheduling an interview that uses a predefined invitation template to generate an email or message, then dispatch it to the candidate's contact information using the appropriate API or messaging service.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically update the candidate's status in the CRM after completing interview steps.
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Create an automation that monitors interview progress and, upon completion of specific steps, triggers an API call to update the candidate's status in the CRM accordingly.

Task Automation.Automated Process: Automatically send the generated interview link to the candidate.
Task Automation.Tools/Comments: Email API, SMS Gateway, Make, Zapier
Task Automation.Detailed Automation Explanation: Set up an automation that, after generating the interview link, automatically sends it to the candidate via their preferred communication channel (email or SMS) using an integrated messaging service.
